<article id="common">
      <title>GT &shortversion;: Common Runtime Components</title>
      <titleabbrev>Common Runtime Components</titleabbrev>
      <para>The common runtime components provide GT4 web and pre-web services with a set of
            libraries and tools that allows these services to be platform independent, to build on
            various abstraction layers (threading, io) and to leverage functionality lower in the
            web services stack (WSRF, WSN, etc).</para>
      <para>See <olink targetdoc="commonKey"/> for more important high-level information about
            common runtime components.</para>
